Ighai tai mua nea siki totobo ge ke pungisia gea siki sakai tana taluutuniana Jesus Christ, na pukuna tai mua liona siki sakai na tinoni ke bosadikalaa nimami na lutu vania God.
Mi tana bona tai sara tana bubulo ni Macedonia ke, me taho tua na malamami na aheahe. Mi tana bona keri, na lei tinoni tara hughuhughu kolughai mara pungisighai, mana ghanaghanamami te mataghu.
